    "20, 21 More recent efforts aim to solve NER and RE simultaneously by building end-to-end models.",
    "[22] [23] [24] [25] This trend has persisted as pretrained large language models (LLMs) have become more accessible.",
    "LLMs have been used for NER/RE tasks in biomedicine, 26 materials, 27 and clinical trials, 28 showing promise as tools for structured data extraction.",
    "For example, Dagdelen et al.",
